reviewText: I think this DVD is well done in terms of representing the respective hunts and the conditions. The scenery is spectacular and overall something enjoyable to watch,

By far the best Alaska hunting DVDs available. Content is real, real Alaskan Trophies are harvested and Billy Molls is the real deal, no Hollywood producing, just real awesome hunting footage that all hunters want to see!
Awesome , the best......If and when I go to  Alaska I will be contacting Mr. Molls. It's real, his videos put you in the hunt.

Once again, completely satisfied with my purchase of Billy Molls videos. This series only gets better and leaves you wanting more. The guide in these videos is top notch and does everything within his power to fulfill his clients wishes and to make them as successful as possible. You will not be disappointed with the acualization of this series. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED....
